{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/tapas/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"e28bfd5e-17d2-5c7d-85c9-314e3748df1f","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://github.com/gazpachu/react-ghost-tapas\" target=\"_blank\">Source code</a>\n</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"Home page\"\n        src=\"/static/e1f284f253794a68b9371b4e841e731d/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e1f284f253794a68b9371b4e841e731d/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/e1f284f253794a68b9371b4e841e731d/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Home page</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Tapas is a Vodafone web blog about Sales, Big Data and Tech insights. It is based on the <a href=\"http://ghost.org/\">Ghost</a> platform.</p>\n<p>In this project, I was in charge of building the front-end, design (except for the logo) and UX. I built a custom React based theme and admin panel using the Ghost API. The header also has an animated particle system based on <a href=\"https://vincentgarreau.com/particles.js/\">Particles.js</a>. There was also as small easter-egg in the footer of every page, which was a rocket that when clicked, would take-off and scroll the page to the top.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"Admin panel - article edit page\"\n        src=\"/static/05580e9f166718380c12ddf0061c9f11/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/05580e9f166718380c12ddf0061c9f11/d1f95/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/05580e9f166718380c12ddf0061c9f11/dbdff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Admin panel - article edit page</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"Admin panel - list of pages and posts\"\n        src=\"/static/079fb9276a3e5a94966b495f53c9959a/dbdff/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/079fb9276a3e5a94966b495f53c9959a/d1f95/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/079fb9276a3e5a94966b495f53c9959a/dbdff/3.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Admin panel - list of pages and posts</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>","fields":{"prefix":"2017"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tapas","categories":"vodafone react redux ghost webpack web ux design inverted","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/b2c5e13bbb2c66e5fa24b256a0a41df6/f3583/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tapas/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}